.Dd December 13, 2014
.Dt WRS 1
.Os wmutils
.Sh NAME
.Nm wrs
.Nd resize windows
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm wrs
.Op Fl a
.Ar x y wid Op ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
resizes the window
.Ar wid
based on the relative pixel values
.Ar x
and
.Ar y .
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl a
Absolute mode. The window will be resized up to the 
.Ar x
and
.Ar y
coordinates.
.El
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Nm
acts on the X display specified by the
.Ev DISPLAY
variable.
